data.description: Welcome to this charming single-story home built in 2006! With 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and 1,108 sq ft of living space, this residence offers comfort and convenience. As a unique perk, it comes with solar panels, which will be paid off at closing and provide you with a considerable saving on your power bills! Step inside and be greeted by a spacious living area perfect for relaxation or entertaining guests. The well-designed kitchen features ample storage and countertop space, making meal preparation a breeze. Retreat to the cozy bedrooms, including a master suite with a private bathroom. This home also boasts a 2-car garage, providing secure parking and additional storage. Located in a friendly neighborhood, and offering energy efficiency with its solar panels, this move-in-ready delight is not just a house, but a smart investment for your future. It is truly a must-see! This listing has a VA assumable loan with 3.75% interest rate!
